description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Capt. Ketcham, Yale 1913 September 13 (date created or published later by Bain) 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title and date from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negatives. Photo shows football player Hank Ketcham (1891-1986) who played varsity football for Yale, 1911-1913 and was captain of the team in 1913. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2010) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication.
